And I learned that lesson when I wrote my
book on the Christian Right.

00:44:33.540 --> 00:44:34.859
HN: Victims of what?

00:44:34.859 --> 00:44:41.349
CH: They are victims of a system that has
cast them aside, crushed their dreams and

