monuments in the city.

00:47:08.720 --> 00:47:14.470
And then he said: "You know, most of these
have been put up in the last 10 years."

00:47:14.470 --> 00:47:18.779
And I said: "That is the exactly what happened
with the breakdown of Yugoslavia."

00:47:18.779 --> 00:47:24.829
All these Yugoslavs suddenly became Serb nationalists
or Croat nationalists.

00:47:24.829 --> 00:47:27.420
CH: I remember being...

00:47:27.420 --> 00:47:29.930
